<plot>Under the guise of showing a script to the sons of Jerry Lewis, Gary and Ronald, Ralph Staub, as he was often prone to do, sneaks in the footage from an old edition of Screen Snapshots when the Photoplay Magazine awards were distributed at a Hollywood dinner several years prior. Seen, again in archive footage, are Martin and Lews, Jimmy Stewart, William Bendix and others. Columbia production number 8857.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?482170</url></doc>
